        "zh": "1.\t遊戲專案團隊組成與工作分配<br>2.\t遊戲專案會議與管理<br>3.\t遊戲開發里程碑之各階段品保測試工作<br>4.\t遊戲品保工作:團隊內測試工作<br>5.\t遊戲品保工作:團隊外測試工作<br>6.\t遊戲錯誤分類與品質評估方法<br>",
        "en": "1.\tCreate working groups and dispatch jobs in game development<br>2.\tManage the progress of game production and meetings<br>3.\tJobs required in quality assurance for each milestone about developing a game project<br>4.\tIntra-team test works on the quality assurance<br>5.\tInter-team test works on the quality assurance<br>6.\tTypes of errors to be corrected and the rapid evaluation method on a game project with its quality assurance<br>"
